OL,3,CSimon Harris 'hopes' Ireland can drop
OL,4,Clegacy legal case against UK Government
OL,6,FThe Taoiseach has said he hopes
OL,7,FIreland will be able to drop its legal
OL,8,Fcase against the UK Government over
OL,9,Flegacy laws.
OL,11,FSimon Harris said he sensed a
OL,12,Fwillingness by the new Labour
OL,13,FGovernment to engage intensively to
OL,14,Ffind a common approach on issues
OL,15,Frelated to the Northern Ireland
OL,16,FTroubles.
