OL,3,CSimon Harris 'hopes' Ireland can drop
OL,4,Clegacy legal case against UK Government
OL,6,FEarlier this week, Northern Ireland
OL,7,FSecretary Hilary Benn set out the
OL,8,FGovernment's plan to repeal and
OL,9,Freplace the previous government's
OL,10,FLegacy Act.
OL,12,FThe Northern Ireland Troubles (Legacy
OL,13,Fand Reconciliation) Act 2023,
OL,14,Fintroduced by the Conservatives,
OL,15,Fhalted scores of civil cases and
OL,16,Finquests into Troubles deaths.
