OL,6,FIt also introduced a provision to give
OL,7,Fconditional immunity to perpetrators
OL,8,Fof Troubles crimes in exchange for
OL,9,Ftheir co-operation with a new truth
OL,10,Frecovery body, the Independent
OL,11,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,12,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).
