OL,3,CSimon Harris 'hopes' Ireland can drop
OL,4,Clegacy legal case against UK Government
OL,6,FThe law was opposed by victims' groups
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland and all the main
OL,8,Fpolitical parties at Stormont. The
OL,9,FIrish Government was also vehemently
OL,10,Fopposed to it and last year initiated
OL,11,Fan interstate legal case against the
OL,12,FUK in the European Court of Human
OL,13,FRights, claiming the Act breached the
OL,14,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,15,F(ECHR).
OL,17,FThe case remains active, with
OL,18,Fministers in Dublin wanting to see how
OL,19,FLabour resolves its concerns over the
OL,20,Flegislation before any decision is
OL,21,Ftaken to withdraw the action.
