OL,3,CSimon Harris 'hopes' Ireland can drop
OL,4,Clegacy legal case against UK Government
OL,6,FAfter attending the British-Irish
OL,7,FCouncil summit in Edinburgh on Friday,
OL,8,FMr Harris spoke of his desire to
OL,9,Fresolve his Government's differences
OL,10,Fwith the UK over legacy.
OL,12,F"The legal action still remains but I
OL,13,Fhope we can get to a position where it
OL,14,Fdoesn't need to remain, but it's
OL,15,Fimportant we get this right," he said.
OL,17,F"I think there's been a lot of hurt, a
OL,18,Flot of broken trust, and I don't mean
OL,19,Fbetween governments, I mean in
OL,20,Frelation to victims, survivors and
OL,21,Ftheir families.
