OL,3,CSimon Harris 'hopes' Ireland can drop
OL,4,Clegacy legal case against UK Government
OL,6,F"There is an opportunity now to deal
OL,7,Fwith a sensitive, a thorny, a
OL,8,Fdifficult, a painful issue. I think
OL,9,Fthere's a willingness, by the way, on
OL,10,Fbehalf of the British Government, the
OL,11,FIrish Government, the parties in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland, to engage and engage
OL,13,Fintensively on this.
OL,15,F"And I hope we can get to a point
OL,16,Fthere where that legal action wouldn't
OL,17,Fbe necessary."
